{
  "stem": "942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here I am in Auschwitz, trying to learn the ropes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] As I mentioned it, there was a hierarchy here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they-- starting from the top down to the block leaders and the, the room leaders-- and their functions were mainly their own self-preservation, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't worry about anybody else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So if a block elder knew that he has, say, I'm not sure-- I can't remember how many people were in a block now, but say, 2,000.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he would go to the kitchen every day and draw rations for 2,000 people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the rations that were really the most worthwhile were the evening meal, when you-- when they drew bread and margarine for us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the rest was liquid stuff only.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they decided, when they received this bread and it was brought down to their room, they decided how thin to slice this bread, you see.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was the scam, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Instead of 10, 10 slices out of a bread, they cut 20 slices.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That meant that they had six, or 10, or how many loaves of bread left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were trading this around, you know, for cigarettes or what have you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I just wanted to tell you that the Polish people who were there, besides that, they were allowed to get a parcel, one parcel a month, you know.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because their families were back at home, you know, where us Jews, you know, we were all-- our families were gone, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had nobody to send us parcels, you see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was the hierarchy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, as I said, they had good clothes, they had handmade, tailored outfits, you know, even though they were stripes.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
